title: Prologue
---
<<declare $lastGrade = "" as string>>
<<declare $lastScore = 0 as number>>
<<declare $cleared   = false as bool>>
<<declare $maxCombo  = 0 as number>>
<<declare $songId    = "" as string>>

<<bg "alley" 0.4>>
<<show "AOBA" "normal" "Left" 0.35 false>>

AOBA: Hey! This is a quick stage test.

Choose what to try:

-> Move test
    <<jump MoveTest>>
-> Expression test
    <<jump ExprTest>>
-> Background test
    <<jump BgTest>>
-> Hide / Show test
    <<jump HideTest>>
-> Play the tutorial song
    <<jump RhythmTest>>
-> End
    <<jump End>>
===

title: MoveTest
---
AOBA: I’ll slide across the stage now.
<<move "AOBA" "Center" 0.35>>
AOBA: Center.
<<move "AOBA" "Right" 0.35>>
AOBA: Right.
<<move "AOBA" "MidLeft" 0.35>>
AOBA: Mid-Left.
<<move "AOBA" "Left" 0.35>>
AOBA: Back to Left.

-> Back to menu
    <<jump Prologue>>
===

title: ExprTest
---
AOBA: Switching expressions…
<<expr "AOBA" "smile" 0.2>>
AOBA: Smile.
<<expr "AOBA" "worry" 0.2>>
AOBA: Worry.
<<expr "AOBA" "normal" 0.2>>
AOBA: Normal.
AOBA: I can flip, too.
<<flip "AOBA" true>>
AOBA: Now facing right.
<<flip "AOBA" false>>
AOBA: And back again.

-> Back to menu
    <<jump Prologue>>
===

title: BgTest
---
AOBA: Let’s change backgrounds.
<<bg "citynight" 0.5>>
AOBA: City night.
<<bg "alley" 0.5>>
AOBA: Back to alley.

-> Back to menu
    <<jump Prologue>>
===

title: HideTest
---
AOBA: Hiding now…
<<hide "AOBA" 0.25>>
(narrator): Character hidden.
<<show "AOBA" "normal" "Left" 0.35 false>>
AOBA: …and shown again.

-> Back to menu
    <<jump Prologue>>
===

title: RhythmTest
---
AOBA: Launching the rhythm tutorial. We’ll return here after.
<<go_to_rhythm "tutorial" "AfterSong">>
===

title: AfterSong
---
<<bg "alley" 0.4>>
<<show "AOBA" "normal" "Left" 0.35 false>>
AOBA: Back from rhythm!
AOBA: song={$songId}  grade={$lastGrade}  score={$lastScore}  maxCombo={$maxCombo}  cleared={$cleared}.

<<jump AfterSong_Choices>>
===

title: AfterSong_Choices
---
-> Back to menu
    <<jump Prologue>>
-> Play again
    <<jump RhythmTest>>
-> End
    <<jump End>>
===

title: End
---
<<hide "AOBA" 0.25>>
(narrator): Done.
<<vn_end>>
===
